ChangeLog for hkauxplot
=================

Version 4.7 - 2015-11-17 (BHP)

- Fixed laTeX bug that caused make doc failure on build.

Version 4.6 - 2014-05-06 (BHP)

- Update to test harness to accommodate testprods
- Fixed bug in making output device XW.
- Reconciliation of dates in docs.
- Reconciled output device logic (in code and params).

Version 4.5.1 - 2014-04-04 (EC)
-------------
- Move withhkauxplot_*.fit from test/ to testprods/hkauxplot_data
- Remove other unused binary test data

Version 4.5 - 2002-07-26 (BHP)
-------------
- New upload as 4.5 for consistency
	
Version 4.4.3 - 2002-07-17 (BHP)
-------------
- Update to accomodate param-2.0
- Updated DEPEND file.
	
Version 4.4.2 - 2002-03-06 (BHP)
-------------
- fixed (another) trivial bug in LaTeX doc
- added GROUPS to hkauxplot.info file.
- minor bug fix in aux arrays.	
	
Version 4.4.1 - 2001-10-31 (UL)
-------------
- fixed trivial bug in LaTeX doc

Version 4.4 - 2001-08-26
-----------

- Added unsigned integer column data type.	

Version 4.3 - 2001-06-06
-----------

- Added total pages to each page (SPR-1866)
- Updated DEPEND file.
	
Version 4.2.3 - 2000-11-30
-----------

- Fixed Makefile in config directory
	
Version 4.2.2 - 2000-11-27
-----------

- Fixed Doc broken links.
- Corrected date format in docs and changelog.	

Version 4.2.1 - 2000-11-17
-----------

- Fixed problem with test harness.
- Added parameter selectoutfile and changed it from useoutfile.
- Added total pages with current page number. 
	
Version 4.2 - 2000-05-26
-----------

- Fixed doc bug. Dspurified input files.

Version 4.1 - 2000-04-26
-----------

- Fixed test harness.
- Added error and warning macros to documentation.	

Version 4.0 - 2000-03-22
-----------

- Close outstanding SPRs.
- Select on rows, frames, time (if applicable). Uses selectlib to
  parse CCDs.	
- New h/k and aux files from real odfs in test harness.
- Layout page for gui.
- More info in title area.	
- More efficient selecting on CCD.
	
Version 3.1 - 1999-08-02
-----------
	
- Addressed several SPRs.
- Changed parameter file dramatically to work better with GUI.	
- Added more error and warning handling.
- Changed plot layout.	
- New version of documentation.
	
Version 3.0 - 1999-06-04
-----------

- Changed name to HKAUXPLOT
- Task now produces plots for Auxiliary Data
- Task allows specification of ODF format for files OR
  full filenames. 
- Task allows for other plot devices than /PS and landscape
  or portrait views.
- Task will actually plot ANY valid x and y columns and will
  allow for no specification of a GTI file. 
- Task will convert ASCII TIME column to real using OAL. 
- Task will convert FRAME counter column to real using OAL. 
- Task will allow input of ANY block for reading plot columns.
- Task supports filename:blockname convension for GTI input file,
  but defaults to STDGTI01.
	
Version 2.1 - 1999-04-16
-----------

- Changed s to f in hkparplot.par file, updated docs, added MB 
  suggestions to test harness.

Version 2.0 - 1999-04-10
-----------

- Fixed bugs, changed parameters, cosmetic output changes,
  added title section, descoped multiple input files, added
  GTI extension selection, added GTI fill area at page bottom,
  added page numbers, addressed SPRs, added time axis offset,
  added clobber parameter.

Version 1.5 - 1998-10-10
-----------

- Parameter changes	
	
Version 1.3 - 1998-06-10
-----------

- Corrected STDIN necessity of test harness (cf SSC-SPR-0186).
	
Version 1.2 - 1998-05-27
-----------

- Time ranges now taken from FITS header.
- Fixed array error problem (cf. SSC-SPR-0023)
- Fixed documentation problems including changing to new format.
- Improved source code comments.

Version 1.1  -  1998-04-29
-----------

- Fixed bugs reported.
- Corrected vague error messages

Version 1.0  -  1998-03-27
	
- Initial version for SAS v1 integration
	
